_aChangeLog.text: Fixed FPS issues in level 2 (thx to juxtapo!)
Moved around triggers and clip brushes

_sText:
This is my second map. 

It's set between two levels, Ice and Fire. 

-Both levels are very easy and the map should only take about 30 seconds to complete on auto, or about 1 minute on scroll.

-Intended to be speedrun on auto, there are a few sweet skips that I'm sure matmo will find in 10 minutes and ruin my map again :^)

Special thanks:
-HUGE thanks to Juxtapo for fixing FPS issues. 

------------------------

V2: 

Fixed FPS problems on the lava stage (thx Juxtapo)

Removed HDR Lighting

Changed around a few triggers and clip brushes 


As a bit of a retrospective, I agree with everyone saying that pologos was better. I made this map with the intention of it being easy; I succeeded in the map being easy but not in it being interesting to play. I've always wanted to make maps with unique designs, so I don't know why I made this one.
